{"body": "@josevalim OK!\r\n\r\nI'll fix and squash it after work.\r\n\r\nJust FYI:\r\nIn my past java experience, and in rare cases, I must have to be different for response header charset and meta tag's charset.\r\n\r\nJava runtime know Windows-31J encoding, and this encoding is necessary for properly character conversion.\r\nBut, it seems that IE6 don't know Windows-31J. We must set Shift_JIS (that is like to Windows-31J) to meta tag's charset ;-)", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/3056315", "created_at": "2011-12-08T01:03:16Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3877#issuecomment-3056315", "updated_at": "2011-12-08T03:58:07Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3877, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/kennyj", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/1f0b221851379759360d7130dabdfa53?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F54ecc28e9508fcf28363014b0d1b4eb8.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/received_events", "gravatar_id": "1f0b221851379759360d7130dabdfa53", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "kennyj", "type": "User", "id": 13426, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5238304bbd3543c15100f60e"}, "id": 3056315, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3877"}
